  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u00a0 \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u00a0 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The condition of an elderly couple from Mannar who went to Dhanushkodi by boat is worrying",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The elderly couple who went to Dhanushkodi by boat from Sri Lanka in the early hours of Monday (27) were rescued from the beach and admitted to the Ramanathapuram District Government Medical College Hospital and are undergoing intensive treatment.",
        "Parameswari and Sivan, an elderly couple from Murunganpitiya, Mannar, traveled to Dhanushkodi by boat from Sri Lanka.",
        "The two were admitted to the Ramanathapuram District Government Medical College Hospital and are receiving intensive care.",
        "District Attorney John Tom Varghese visited the two men in medical treatment and instructed them to carry out the necessary medical treatment.",
        "He was referred to Madurai Government Rajaji Hospital as his health was critical.",
        "More than 85 people have so far fled to Tamil Nadu as refugees due to the severe economic crisis in Sri Lanka.",
        "Parameswari and Sivan, an elderly couple from Murunganpitiya, Mannar, landed at Dhanushkodi beach near Rameshwaram this morning (27).",
        "It is noteworthy that the two have been found lying unconscious on the beach."
      ],
